 式），激波跳跃关系
\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
condition!jump ~
\end_layout

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\eval{\ket{U}}_{-}^{+}u_{\Gamma}=\eval{\ket{F}}_{-}^{+}
\]

\end_inset

等价于
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}(u_{1}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{1} & =(u_{2}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{2}\\
(u_{1}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{1}u_{1}+p_{1} & =(u_{2}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{2}u_{2}+p_{2}\\
(u_{1}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{1}E_{1}+p_{1}u_{1} & =(u_{2}-u_{\Gamma})\rho_{2}E_{2}+p_{2}u_{2}
\end{aligned}
\label{eq:euler_1d_jump}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $u_{\Gamma}$
\end_inset

 为间断面移动速度。如果定义「相对速度」 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{i}=u_{i}-u_{\Gamma}$
\end_inset

，则 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:euler_1d_jump"

\end_inset

 式可化为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
\begin{aligned}\rho_{1}v_{1} & =\rho_{2}v_{2}\\
\rho_{1}v_{1}^{2}+p_{1} & =\rho_{2}v_{2}^{2}+p_{2}\\
h_{1}+v_{1}^{2}/2 & =h_{2}+v_{2}^{2}/2
\end{aligned}
\label{eq:euler_1d_jump_in_relative_speed}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

其中 
\begin_inset Formula $h=e+p/\rho$
\end_inset

 为「比焓 (specific enthalpy)」。
